# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
# The app is a client-side-routed SPA (React Router). Without this, a hard
# navigation or refresh on a client route (e.g. /discover, reached via the
# landing page's "Start browsing" button which does window.top.location.href
# = '/discover') makes Pages look for a file at that path, 404, and serve a
# broken shell. Rewrite every non-asset path to index.html so the router can
# take over. Real files (/assets/*, /landing.html, etc.) still win over this.
/*    /index.html   200
